{
  "blank_canvas": true,
  "description": [
    "<h1><span class='warning'>Important:</span> Simple print example</h1>",
    "<p>This simple exercise is to help you learn what to",
    "    expect when Reeborg has to write something but gets ",
    "    it wrong. First, the program that produces the correct",
    "    result.</p>",
    "<pre class='python'>",
    "print(\"Hello!\")",
    "print(\"My name is Reeborg.\")",
    "</pre>",
    "<p>If you use Javascript, replace <code>print()</code> by",
    "    <code>writeln()</code>.</p>",
    "<p>Run the program above. After doing that, make the following",
    "    changes, and run it again.</p>",
    "<ol><li>Change a single letter in what is to be written.</li>",
    "    <li>Change an entire word.</li>",
    "    <li>Add an empty print statement, <code>print()</code></li>",
    "    <ll>Put all the text in a single print statement, with no",
    "        newline character, <code>\\n</code> added.</li>",
    "    <li>Do not print anything.</li>",
    "</ol>",
    "DIFFICULTY1"
  ],
  "post": [
    "RUR.public.check_output()"
  ],
  "onload": [
    "RUR.show_description();",
    "// define a function that can be called,",
    "// in the Post editor for programs written",
    "// using either Python or Javascript.",
    "RUR.public.check_output = function () {",
    "    var actual = RUR.get_print();",
    "    var expected = \"Hello!\\nMy name is Reeborg.\\n\";",
    "    var output;",
    "    ",
    "    if (actual == expected) {",
    "        throw new RUR.ReeborgOk(\"Well done!\");",
    "    }",
    "    if (actual == '') {",
    "        output = RUR.show_detailed_diff(expected, actual,",
    "               {semantic: true, show_actual: true,",
    "               actual_heading : \"<span class='warning'>Nothing was printed!</span>\"});",
    "    } else {",
    "        output = RUR.show_detailed_diff(expected, actual,",
    "                               {semantic: true});",
    "    }",
    "    ",
    "    throw new RUR.ReeborgError(output);",
    "};"
  ],
  "small_tiles": false,
  "rows": 12,
  "cols": 14
}